<A>__{ as he blows it. a sidelong glance at the pillar? a sudden naked hunger in the smiling eyes? a single bead of sweat? some tiny little thing that takes the lid off his game. terri stops dead. she doesn't know what's happening but suddenly this doesn't feel right.}
