<A>__{terri safely feet away from the pillar stands, shaking and breathless, eyes wide in horror and shock as she stares at this creature from nightmare. and suddenly pinhead changes tack; he slides from the roaring beast of a moment before to his more usual persona the glib, articulate black pope of hell.}
